<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Fee Standards are set according to Article 10 of the Charges and Fees Act.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Maintenance fees for the performance venue, exhibition rooms as well as conference rooms of the National Taiwan Arts Education Center are charged as follows:
1. Maintenance Fee Standards for Performance Venues (As attachment 1)
2. Maintenance Fee Standards for Exhibition Rooms (As attachment 2)
3. Maintenance Fee Standards for Conference Rooms (As attachment 3)]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The fees set forth in the standard are stipulated by taking such factors as maintenance costs for equipment in the venues and facilities as well as the consumer price index into consideration.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This standard shall take effect on the day of promulgation.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
